Description: Aker Carbon Capture ASA is a pure play carbon capture company based in Norway. The Company has a technology to enable carbon emission reductions in hard-to-abate sectors such as waste incineration, bio-energy, cement, gas to power and many other industries. The Companyâ€™s activities are divided into four segments: Cement production, Bio or waste to energy generation, Gas to power and Blue hydrogen. The Company operates in Norway, Denmark and the United Kingdom.
